			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>So your argument for chapter length is based off of a book designed to hold a child&#8217;s attention span&#8230; I do have to say, as an educator and someone that puts a lot of weight into being able to explicitly filling out your own voice into stories, I can tell you that I would tell every one of my students to ignore this type of advice.</p>
